{
  "info": {
    "name": "Gudang Planet — POS API (v1.9)",
    "description": "Collection untuk modul POS Gudang Planet (perubahan v1.9 + marketing v2).\n\n**Base URL:** `{{base_url}}/api/v1`\n\n**Auth:** Bearer token dari `POST /api/v1/login`\n\n**Credential demo:**\n| Role | Phone | Password |\n|------|-------|----------|\n| KASIR | 087777888888 | kasir_gp |\n| ADMIN | 081122223333 | admin_gp |\n\n**Marketing v2:**\n- Picker POS: `GET /marketings` (read-only)\n- CRUD: `POST /api/v1/operational/marketings` (collection OPS terpisah)\n- Transaksi wajib/isian `marketing_uuid` — role: MARKETING_LEAD, MARKETING, MARKETING_TETAP\n\n**Header:**\n- `Accept: application/json`\n- `Accept-Language: {{lang}}` (id/en)\n- `Authorization: Bearer {{token}}`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8000", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "lang", "value": "id", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "product_uuid", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "transaction_ulid", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "installment_ulid", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "detail_ulid", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "customer_uuid", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "marketing_uuid", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "marketing_lead_uuid", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "return_ulid", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [{ "key": "token", "value": "{{token}}", "type": "string" }]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.token) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{lang}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"087777888888\",\n  \"password\": \"kasir_gp\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/login",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "login"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Product (v1.9 — New Pricing Fields)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create Product",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{lang}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Produk Contoh\",\n  \"code\": \"PRD-001\",\n  \"base_price\": 20000,\n  \"leader_price\": 25000,\n  \"marketing_price\": 26000,\n  \"sell_price\": 30000,\n  \"category_id\": 1,\n  \"unit_id\": 1,\n  \"stock\": 100,\n  \"min_stock\": 10,\n  \"description\": \"Produk contoh untuk testing\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/products",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "products"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Products",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{lang}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/products",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "products"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Product",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{lang}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Produk Contoh Updated\",\n  \"base_price\": 18000,\n  \"leader_price\": 23000,\n  \"marketing_price\": 24000,\n  \"sell_price\": 28000,\n  \"stock\": 90\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/products/{{product_uuid}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "products", "{{product_uuid}}"]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Marketing (v2 — Picker & Reports)",
      "description": "Modul marketing di POS bersifat **read-only** (picker transaksi + laporan komisi).\n\n**CRUD marketing** (MARKETING_LEAD / MARKETING + assign `leader_uuid`) dilakukan di OPS:\n`POST/PATCH/DELETE /api/v1/operational/marketings`\n\n**Role picker transaksi:** `MARKETING_LEAD`, `MARKETING`, `MARKETING_TETAP`\n\n**Response field penting:**\n- `role` — tipe marketing\n- `leader` — diisi jika role `MARKETING` (lead induknya)\n\n**Catatan komisi:**\n- `MARKETING` → lead & marketing dapat komisi\n- `MARKETING_LEAD` → lead dapat komisi\n- `MARKETING_TETAP` → tidak masuk laporan komisi POS (bonus via absensi)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Marketings",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (json.data && json.data.length > 0 && json.data[0].uuid) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('marketing_uuid', json.data[0].uuid);",
                  "    const lead = json.data.find((row) => row.role === 'MARKETING_LEAD');",
                  "    if (lead) pm.collectionVariables.set('marketing_lead_uuid', lead.uuid);",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{lang}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/marketings?per_page=15&order_by_key=name&order_by_value=ASC",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "marketings"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "per_page", "value": "15" },
                { "key": "order_by_key", "value": "name" },
                { "key": "order_by_value", "value": "ASC" },
                { "key": "search", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "role", "value": "", "disabled": true, "description": "MARKETING_LEAD | MARKETING | MARKETING_TETAP" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Daftar marketing untuk picker transaksi penjualan (kasir/admin)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Marketings — MARKETING",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{lang}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/marketings?role=MARKETING",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "marketings"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "role", "value": "MARKETING" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Marketings — MARKETING_LEAD",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{lang}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/marketings?role=MARKETING_LEAD",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "marketings"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "role", "value": "MARKETING_LEAD" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Marketings — MARKETING_TETAP",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{lang}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/marketings?role=MARKETING_TETAP",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "marketings"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "role", "value": "MARKETING_TETAP" }
              ]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Show Marketing",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{lang}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/marketings/{{marketing_uuid}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "marketings", "{{marketing_uuid}}"]
            },
            "description": "Detail marketing termasuk `role` dan `leader` (jika role MARKETING)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Report — Marketing Commission (All)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{lang}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/reports/marketing-commission?date_from=2026-06-01&date_to=2026-06-30",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "reports", "marketing-commission"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "date_from", "value": "2026-06-01" },
                { "key": "date_to", "value": "2026-06-30" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Laporan komisi MARKETING + MARKETING_LEAD. MARKETING_TETAP tidak termasuk."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Report — Marketing Commission (By UUID)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Accept-Language", "value": "{{lang}}" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/reports/marketing-commission?date_from=2026-06-01&date_to=2026-06-30&marketing_uuid={{marketing_uuid}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "reports", "marketing-commission"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "date_from", "value": "2026-06-01" },
                { "key": "date_to", "value": "2026-06-30" },
                { "key": "marketing_uuid", "value": "{{marketing_uuid}}" }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Sales Transaction (v1.9 — Down Payment + Marketing)",
      "item": [
